## 📈 Performance Characteristics

### Typical Execution Times

| Operation | Average Time | P95 | P99 |
|-----------|--------------|-----|-----|
| Inventory Deduction | 20-50ms | 80ms | 100ms |
| Stock Addition | 20-50ms | 80ms | 100ms |
| Stock Query | 5-15ms | 30ms | 50ms |
| Full Order Creation | 100-200ms | 300ms | 500ms |

### Performance Factors

**Fast Operations:**
- ✅ Indexed queries (product_id, tenant_id)
- ✅ Row-level locking (not table-level)
- ✅ Connection pooling
- ✅ JPA dirty checking (no explicit save needed)

**Potential Bottlenecks:**
- ⚠️ Lock contention (multiple threads)
- ⚠️ Network latency (database connection)
- ⚠️ Transaction timeout (long-running operations)
- ⚠️ Database load (concurrent users)

